For #mentalhealthmonth, @OfficialWondermind is working to destigmatize mental health by empowering you to share your story. Thanks for sharing! #letswondermind

It’s finally here—the @officialwondermind newsletter is live! Subscribe at the link in my bio to read the first issue where I open up about my own mental health journey. Let’s democratize and destigmatize mental fitness together! #letswondermind

Our first initiative for @officialwondermind will be an email newsletter dedicated to taking time for your mind! The first issue will be coming very soon so make sure to subscribe at the link in my bio #letswondermind
@officialwondermind is coming soon! Sign up at the link in my bio so you can be the first to know the official launch date
Let Somebody Go with @Coldplay Video premieres Monday 5pm GMT, 6pm CET, Noon ET, 9am PT

As we kick off a new year, it’s important that we set an intention around our well-being. I’m so excited to be partnering with @Google, a Rare Impact Fund contributor, to judge this year’s #DoodleforGoogle student art contest. This year’s prompt, “I care for myself by…” is especially meaningful to me. I can’t wait to learn how students across the country are approaching mental health and self-care. Visit goo.gle/D4G22 for more info on how to submit. #GooglePartner #GoogleDoodle

The best reminder of why we do what we do @rarebeauty 💌 I’m so happy I was able to surprise everyone at our fourth annual Mental Health Summit yesterday. 

We heard from some of the brightest minds in mental health-from experts to members of our community. Bringing these people together under one roof is truly one of my favorite experiences every year. 

Thank you to my Rare Beauty team for all the incredible work you do, and thank you to our speakers: @ecohen817 @jayshetty @dr.thema @tdehealth @drjennytaitz @heartofmeena  @tel_beloved_community @latinxtherapy @latinxtherapist @a_million_myles @translifeline @Ia2050 @jud.ithmartinez @drjessigold @branchspeaks @everforwardclub @cynth_pop @tarasigari @drkatiehurleylcsw @jedfoundation @katiewelch @L2SMentalHealth
